org.apache.hadoop.hive.accumulo.predicate.compare

Interface PrimitiveComparison

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleCompare, IntCompare, LongCompare, StringCompare

    public interface PrimitiveComparison
    Wraps type-specific comparison operations over a constant value. Methods take raw byte from incoming Accumulo values. The CompareOpt instance in the iterator uses one or more methods from a PrimitiveCompare implementation to perform type-specific comparisons and determine acceptances. Used by PrimitiveComparisonFilter. Works with CompareOp
